<html>
  <head>
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dosis:wght@300;400;500&amp;family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&amp;display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&amp;display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />

    <style>
      :root {
  --ganesa-blue: #233548;
  --ganesa-dark-red: #741e18;
  --ganesa-light-red: #b23237;
  --ganesa-white: #f4f4f4;
  --ganesa-golden: #dd9a42;
  --ganesa-black: #202227; }

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box; }

@media (max-width: 1080px) {
  html {
    font-size: 93.75%; } }

@media (max-width: 720px) {
  html {
    font-size: 87.5%; } }

body {
  background: var(--background);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialised;
  padding: 16px; }

body,
input,
textarea,
button {
  font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  background: #f4f4f4; }

h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6,
strong {
  font-weight: 600; }

strong {
  color: var(--ganesa-light-red); }

button {
  cursor: pointer; }

h2 {
  font-family: "Dosis";
  font-size: 26px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 16px; }
  h2 span {
    color: var(--ganesa-light-red); }

p {
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  line-height: 22px; }

.att {
  margin-top: 16px; }

table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin-top: 16px;
  margin: 32px auto;
  width: fit-content;
  width: 80%; }
  table td {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0; }
    table td:first-of-type {
      margin-top: 1rem; }
    table td:last-of-type {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-evenly; }
  table tbody > tr {
    transition: background 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 -1px 0 0 var(--ganesa-black); }
    table tbody > tr:hover {
      background: #e3e3e3; }
  table th {
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--ganesa-light-red); }
  table svg {
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    background: transparent; }
    table svg:hover {
      transform: scale(1.2);
      filter: brightness(0.8); }

.total {
  display: block;
  margin: 16px auto; }

  footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ganesa-light-red);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--ganesa-blue);
    border-color: var(--ganesa-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

    </style>

    <title>Ganesa T.I. - Implantação</title>
  </head>
    <body>
        <h2>Olá, <span>{{nome}}</span>!</h2>
        <p>
          Viemos por meio deste informar acerca dos documentos em aberto abaixo listados.
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Documento</th>
                  <th>Tipo do Documento</th>
                  <th>Valor Total</th>
                  <th>Valor Pago</th>
                  <th>Vencimento</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                  {{#each documentos}}
                  <tr>
                    <td>{{id}}</td>
                    <td>{{TIPODOCTO}}</td>
                    <td>{{VALORTOTAL}}</td>
                    <td>{{VALORPAGO}}</td>
                    <td>{{DATAVENCIMENTO}}</td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/each}}
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <span class="total"><strong>Valor Total: </strong>{{valorTotalSelecionado}}</span>
            <p>

            Nos colocamos à disposição para esclarecimento de eventuais dúvidas através deste e-mail ou no
            fone <strong>{{empresaTelefone}}</strong>.<br/>
            </p>
            <p class="att">
              Atenciosamente,<br/>
              <strong>
                {{empresaNome}}
              </strong>
            </p>
        </p>
        <footer>
          <p>Desenvolvidor por <a href="https://www.ganesa.com.br">Ganesa Tecnologia &mdash; Sistemas e T.I. Corporativa</a></p>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
